Author: rhymeswithpanda1987
Text: Exercising at 11PM to burn off extra calories is weird? :p

Author: SpaceWhale88
Text: I get it. Last time I lost weight I got so many compliments but people didn't understand that food and calories had taken over my life. I once ate 7 taco chips I didn't have the calories for so I went for a run at 11pm to burn it off. But runs are healthy yay!
